(24, 'The Boys Season 1', 'A group of vigilantes known informally as “The Boys” set out to take down corrupt superheroes with no more than blue-collar grit and a willingness to fight dirty.', 2019, 'Sci-Fi & Fantasy, Action & Adventure', 8.0, '../../uploads/The Boys.jpg', '', 'Dan Trachtenberg', 1, '2024-08-13 14:29:45', '1'),
