(11, 'A Delicate Relationship', 'Ani', ' Adult , Ecchi , Mature , Smut , Drama , Office Workers , Romance', 'Complete', 2023, 'Whatever, Geezer.\' Jaewon was insulted by his neighbor who was smoking a cigarette. He swore that if he encounters her again, he will kill her. That girl turns out to be a new part-time worker at his company?! She\'s even his best friend’s girlfriend?! What\'s going on?!', 8.0, '../../uploads/A Delicate Relationship.jpeg', 1, '2024-09-03'),
(12, 'A Different Class', 'Baby', ' Adult , Mature , Smut , College life , Comedy , Harem , Romance', 'Complete', 2021, 'Hwan returns to college after his military service, and runs into a mess involving his first love, his ex and even a freshman. His life is a total chaos between the girls who are out to get him!', 8.0, '../../uploads/A Different Class.jpeg', 1, '2024-09-03'),
(13, 'A Good Day To Pitch A Tent', '  Heart', '  Drama, Romance', 'Complete', 2022, 'Six months in to their marriage, Youngsu and his wife, has no time for sex because his wife is too busy with work. One day, they decide to do some camping to relieve some stress and maybe to address their marital troubles. But then Youngsu got into a mess with a woman… and not his wife!\r\n\r\nA Good Day To Pitch A Tent Manhwa also known as A Good Day To Camp. This end webtoon was released in 2021. This series was written by Heart and illustrations by Blank. A Good Day To Pitch A Tent Webtoon is about Drama, Romance story.', 8.0, '../../uploads/A-Good-Day-To-Camp-Manhwa-ToonGod-193x278.jpg', 1, '2024-09-03'),
(14, 'A Knowing Sister', 'City girl / Dosinyeo', 'Adult , Ecchi , Mature , Smut , Romance', 'Complete', 2020, 'So that girl finally grew up? My neighbor Jieun suddenly came to share my room and motivate me sexually. I am Haeyoung, a student who is motivated because I will finally be able to have sex with my girlfriend Senna, after a long relationship.', 8.0, '../../uploads/A Knowing Sister.jpeg', 1, '2024-09-03'),
(15, 'A Pervert\'s Daily Life Season 1', 'Alice crazy', 'Adult , Ecchi , Mature , Smut , Comedy , Full Color , Harem , Romance', 'Complete', 2019, 'Shin Seyoung just got accepted in the company thus started living in the employee\'s dormitory. On her first day of moving she accidentally went to the wrong room and saw her mentor masturbating! What will be of Shin Seyoung when she awakened her dirty side after the incident?', 9.0, '../../uploads/A Pervert\'s Daily Life Season 1.jpeg', 1, '2024-09-03'),
(16, 'A Sensitive Issue', 'Gaehoju', 'Adult , Mature , Smut , Comedy , Drama , Full Color , Office Workers , Psychological , Romance', 'Complete', 2021, 'Minjoon has a very peculiar condition: he’s hypersensitive to the point where he gets turned on by women constantly. Even the mere sound of a woman breathing next to him can get him worked up. So he’s built a life avoiding women, even to the point of picking a job on a team where there’s only men. Except, that carefully built life is at risk when Sumin is assigned to his team. Now, Minjoon must navigate his way through the office with a gorgeous coworker', 8.0, '../../uploads/A Sensitive Issue.jpeg', 1, '2024-09-03'),
(17, 'A Twisted Day', 'Giri / Taegam', ' Adult , Mature , Drama , Romance', 'Complete', 2021, 'Ji-han, who has made a successful investment, bought three small suites and became a young landlord. Unexpectedly, he met yo nari from the same class in high school who used to bully him….', 8.0, '../../uploads/A Twisted Day.jpeg', 1, '2024-09-03'),
(18, 'A Wise Driver’s Life', 'Kkeondae', 'Adult , Mature , Smut , Drama , Fantasy , Full Color , Romance', 'Ongoing', 2023, 'Woojin is the sole male employee at his kindergarten. His main responsibility is to drive the school bus. One day, while managing the kindergarten’s app, he discovers a fascinating function… “I can manage the teachers and students’ parents? Seems like life at the kindergarten is going to be fun going forward.”\r\n\r\nA Wise Driver’s Life Manhwa also known as 슬기로운 기사생활. This on-going webtoon was released in 2023. This series was written by Kkeondae and illustrations by Baekji. A Wise Driver’s Life Webtoon is about Drama, Fantasy, Harem story.', 9.0, '../../uploads/A Wise Driver’s Life.jpeg', 1, '2024-09-03'),
